---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
import Line from "./Line.astro";
---

<h3>Consider hosting an event at Rosenhøj for an unforgettable experience.</h3>
<section>
  <img src="../images/Events2.png" alt="Events" />
  <p>
    With vintage-inspired surroundings and the ability to cater to up to 40 guests, we offer an ideal setting for any occasion - whether it's a confirmation, birthday party, or company event. <br />
    <br />
    Our expert chef will craft delicious menus to meet your specific preferences and dietary requirements. Whether you desire a formal dinner or a casual buffet, we can cater to your needs with high-quality cuisine and exceptional service.
  </p>

  <img src="../images/Events1.png" alt="Events" />

  <p>
    Our dedicated team will assist you in every aspect of planning, including table settings, decor, music, and entertainment, to ensure your event is a resounding success. We pride ourselves on delivering outstanding service and attention to detail,
    so you can relax and enjoy your special occasion. <br /><br />Get in touch with us today to learn more about our event packages and menu options. We'd be honored to host your next special event at Rosenhøj.
  </p>
</section>
<Button text="CONTACT US" link="" />

<style>
  section {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: auto;
  }
  h3 {
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--dark_blue);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 5vw, 2rem);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  p {
    margin-inline: 2.5em;
    margin-block: 2em;
    font-family: "raleway", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: normal;
    line-height: 150%;
  }

  img {
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 450px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: bottom;
  }
  @media (min-width: 800px) {
    section {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1300px;
    }
    p {
      max-width: 55ch;
      padding-block: 2rem;
      font-size: 1.5vw;
    }

    h2 {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
    img:first-of-type,
    p:nth-of-type(2),
    p:nth-of-type(3) {
      grid-column: 2/3;
    }
    img:last-of-type,
    p:first-of-type {
      grid-column: 1/2;
    }
    img:first-of-type,
    p:first-of-type {
      grid-row: 2/3;
    }
    img:last-of-type {
      grid-row: span 2;
    }
  }
</style>
